Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:42.78,o-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.06,o-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}優しくね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:49.32,o-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}でも　負けられないよ　はい
